WEBVTT

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:11.000
I love you, Ping.

00:00:11.766 --> 00:00:12.933
I've been waiting for you all this time.

00:00:13.600 --> 00:00:15.166
Could you give me a chance, Ping?

00:00:15.933 --> 00:00:19.500
Charm was drugged by my friend, Mint.

00:00:19.733 --> 00:00:21.533
But absolutely nothing happened between them.

00:00:21.900 --> 00:00:23.500
Mint told me so herself.

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:26.000
Charm just fell asleep.

00:00:27.166 --> 00:00:27.966
P'Charm.

00:00:28.966 --> 00:00:30.100
How did you get here?

00:00:30.966 --> 00:00:32.106
Come with me.

00:00:32.947 --> 00:00:33.912
Please?

00:00:34.940 --> 00:00:36.293
Just for tonight is fine.

00:00:40.566 --> 00:00:41.138
Ping.

00:00:42.633 --> 00:00:44.520
Ever since you ran away from me,

00:00:45.268 --> 00:00:46.437
there hasn't been a single day

00:00:46.811 --> 00:00:48.382
that I didn't think about you.

00:00:49.363 --> 00:00:51.390
No matter how much time passes,

00:00:52.932 --> 00:00:54.127
I'll still wait.

00:01:01.133 --> 00:01:03.000
You've been using the Charmie IG account.

00:01:07.466 --> 00:01:09.102
You've missed me

00:01:10.935 --> 00:01:12.597
all this time too, haven't you?

00:01:18.166 --> 00:01:19.666
Wait, you knew?

00:01:21.966 --> 00:01:22.766
I did.

00:01:26.366 --> 00:01:28.166
But I wanted to hear it from you.

00:01:31.066 --> 00:01:32.700
Do you really love Khun Pat?

00:01:34.766 --> 00:01:36.366
If you really love him,

00:01:36.933 --> 00:01:37.800
I'll back off.

00:01:40.666 --> 00:01:42.366
But if you still love me...

00:02:59.300 --> 00:03:00.533
I love you, Ping.

00:03:01.300 --> 00:03:02.100
So much.

00:03:03.333 --> 00:03:05.666
I could never love anyone else.

00:04:52.566 --> 00:04:53.213
Ouch!

00:04:54.288 --> 00:04:55.587
P'Charm!

00:04:56.148 --> 00:04:57.547
Am I fat?

00:05:00.366 --> 00:05:01.400
Just a bit chubby.

00:05:07.733 --> 00:05:08.566
This part is soft.

00:05:13.300 --> 00:05:14.266
And here too.

00:05:20.333 --> 00:05:21.200
Are you teasing me?

00:05:31.900 --> 00:05:33.200
I'm not.

00:05:34.733 --> 00:05:35.533
I'm serious.

00:05:37.000 --> 00:05:38.066
Are you really?

00:05:39.966 --> 00:05:40.766
Then...

00:05:45.400 --> 00:05:46.566
go for it.

00:05:52.900 --> 00:05:54.000
Aren't you taking it off?

00:06:11.133 --> 00:06:12.066
I already did.

00:06:13.100 --> 00:06:14.100
What about you?

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:16.900
I can't really get it off myself.

00:06:22.200 --> 00:06:23.733
You'll have to help me.

00:07:23.166 --> 00:07:24.100
You're awake?

00:07:46.133 --> 00:07:46.950
Ping.

00:07:50.000 --> 00:07:51.461
From now on,

00:07:53.797 --> 00:07:55.925
I'll never make you cry again.

00:07:58.966 --> 00:08:00.536
No matter what happens,

00:08:02.779 --> 00:08:04.267
I'll be right here,

00:08:06.277 --> 00:08:07.488
by your side,

00:08:08.610 --> 00:08:10.275
forever.

00:08:28.200 --> 00:08:29.601
I'm so glad

00:08:30.536 --> 00:08:32.934
we get to shower together like this again.

00:08:35.333 --> 00:08:36.203
Then...

00:08:37.138 --> 00:08:39.647
how about you shower me every day, P'Charm?

00:08:49.700 --> 00:08:51.666
I really missed your scent.

00:08:53.700 --> 00:08:56.366
I missed yours too, P'Charm.

00:08:57.900 --> 00:08:58.700
Give me a kiss.

00:09:38.400 --> 00:09:40.015
The evening light like this...

00:09:41.978 --> 00:09:43.808
is so beautiful.

00:09:45.466 --> 00:09:46.966
It looks just like a painting.

00:09:53.133 --> 00:09:54.133
You know what, Ping?

00:09:56.200 --> 00:09:57.500
For the past five years,

00:10:00.500 --> 00:10:02.766
every time I saw the sunset,

00:10:04.333 --> 00:10:05.800
I always hoped

00:10:07.266 --> 00:10:08.733
that when I woke up,

00:10:11.300 --> 00:10:13.000
you'd be right beside me.

00:10:16.500 --> 00:10:17.966
Thank you, P'Charm,

00:10:20.333 --> 00:10:22.266
for always keeping your promise.

00:10:23.933 --> 00:10:24.766
I promise

00:10:26.900 --> 00:10:28.829
that every second from now on,

00:10:30.558 --> 00:10:32.642
I'll spend it

00:10:34.604 --> 00:10:36.332
making the most of it with you.

00:10:37.733 --> 00:10:38.746
I love you, Ping.

00:10:42.366 --> 00:10:43.533
You know, P'Charm?

00:10:45.400 --> 00:10:47.733
When you actually say the word "love",

00:10:49.300 --> 00:10:50.700
it gives me butterflies every time.

00:10:54.466 --> 00:10:55.332
Then...

00:10:55.939 --> 00:10:58.073
should I say it to you every day?

00:11:04.966 --> 00:11:06.287
I really don't know

00:11:08.530 --> 00:11:10.166
what tomorrow will bring,

00:11:11.755 --> 00:11:13.383
but today I know that

00:11:15.065 --> 00:11:16.440
I have you,

00:11:18.933 --> 00:11:20.500
and that makes me so happy.

00:11:24.533 --> 00:11:26.081
I promise you,

00:11:27.950 --> 00:11:29.239
that from now on,

00:11:30.687 --> 00:11:32.555
no matter how many times the sun sets,

00:11:34.518 --> 00:11:36.367
I'll be right by your side.

00:11:38.400 --> 00:11:40.600
And we'll face every new morning together.

00:12:40.366 --> 00:12:43.100
I came here today to talk about the engagement.

00:12:44.600 --> 00:12:46.655
I'm so sorry, Ploen.

00:12:46.935 --> 00:12:49.846
Ping suddenly fell ill today.

00:12:50.533 --> 00:12:51.333
Oh, really?

00:12:59.733 --> 00:13:02.600
It's alright, dear.
We can always come back another time.

00:13:03.166 --> 00:13:06.300
Get the car ready right now.
I'm going to Khun Ping's condo.

00:13:11.166 --> 00:13:12.466
Thank you, P'Charm.

00:13:13.200 --> 00:13:15.366
Give me some time to sort out my own things first.

00:13:16.500 --> 00:13:18.200
Do you really not want me there with you?

00:13:20.300 --> 00:13:22.900
I'm not afraid to face your parents.

00:13:24.300 --> 00:13:25.766
I genuinely want to talk to them.

00:13:27.300 --> 00:13:28.600
Just give me some time.

00:13:33.333 --> 00:13:35.100
I'm going up to my room now, P'Charm.

00:13:58.400 --> 00:13:59.180
Ping, sweetheart.

00:13:59.554 --> 00:14:00.571
Where have you been?

00:14:03.235 --> 00:14:05.821
Ploen, Pat, and I have been waiting for you all day.

00:14:06.335 --> 00:14:07.868
You didn't answer your phone.

00:14:08.616 --> 00:14:11.261
An engagement isn't something to take lightly.

00:14:12.866 --> 00:14:14.066
I'm sorry, Mom.

00:14:14.766 --> 00:14:16.266
I know you mean well.

00:14:16.700 --> 00:14:18.466
But I don't love P'Pat.

00:14:20.166 --> 00:14:22.300
I don't want to marry someone I don't love.

00:14:23.266 --> 00:14:24.200
Then who do you love?

00:14:24.700 --> 00:14:26.666
Don't tell me it's that woman.

00:14:27.100 --> 00:14:29.733
The one who broke your heart and made you move abroad?

00:14:30.766 --> 00:14:31.566
Yes.

00:14:32.733 --> 00:14:34.033
I love P'Charm.

00:14:34.033 --> 00:14:34.600
Ping.

00:14:35.866 --> 00:14:37.266
Think this through.

00:14:37.700 --> 00:14:40.466
That woman broke your heart before.

00:14:40.933 --> 00:14:43.100
Why would you go back to someone like her?

00:14:43.266 --> 00:14:44.600
But it wasn't like that, Mom.

00:14:45.766 --> 00:14:47.133
I know the whole truth now.

00:14:48.500 --> 00:14:50.566
It was all a misunderstanding on my part.

00:14:51.800 --> 00:14:53.900
P'Charm never cheated on me.

00:14:56.800 --> 00:14:57.600
Mom.

00:14:59.266 --> 00:15:00.466
I've made my choice.

00:15:01.800 --> 00:15:03.500
I don't want to waste any more time.

00:15:11.766 --> 00:15:13.133
I'm tired, Ping.

00:15:15.533 --> 00:15:17.866
Let's talk about this some other day.

00:15:24.466 --> 00:15:26.466
I'm sorry for letting you down.

00:15:28.966 --> 00:15:30.802
But I want to spend my life

00:15:31.550 --> 00:15:33.848
with the person I choose.

00:15:47.866 --> 00:15:48.666
Mom...

00:16:17.100 --> 00:16:18.441
Is everything alright?

00:16:19.142 --> 00:16:21.240
You've looked stressed for days now.

00:16:21.866 --> 00:16:24.165
It's about our daughter, Ping.

00:16:25.240 --> 00:16:29.092
Did you know she's calling it off with Pat?

00:16:29.699 --> 00:16:31.942
And she said she already loves someone else.

00:16:31.942 --> 00:16:34.574
Another woman.

00:16:36.100 --> 00:16:37.107
I know.

00:16:37.668 --> 00:16:38.961
I know everything.

00:16:39.500 --> 00:16:40.473
You knew?

00:16:40.660 --> 00:16:44.453
And you're just sitting there? This is a big deal!

00:16:45.200 --> 00:16:46.984
I just think that our daughter

00:16:46.984 --> 00:16:48.046
is grown up now.

00:16:48.280 --> 00:16:50.113
She has her own life.

00:16:50.674 --> 00:16:53.667
How can we force anyone's heart, Khun Pi?

00:16:54.733 --> 00:16:57.172
So you expect me to just accept

00:16:57.406 --> 00:16:59.767
that our daughter is dating a woman?

00:17:00.328 --> 00:17:03.701
Then we won't ever get the chance
to hold our grandchildren.

00:17:06.100 --> 00:17:07.444
I understand you.

00:17:07.631 --> 00:17:08.810
The grandchild thing

00:17:08.997 --> 00:17:10.060
is a big deal.

00:17:10.294 --> 00:17:14.494
But I don't think it's as important as
our daughter's happiness.

00:17:15.300 --> 00:17:18.025
The world has changed a lot now.

00:17:18.492 --> 00:17:21.249
When it comes to family and having kids,

00:17:21.670 --> 00:17:24.550
technology can help these days.

00:17:24.924 --> 00:17:26.156
It doesn't have to be a man and a woman

00:17:26.156 --> 00:17:29.554
to build a happy family.

00:17:32.133 --> 00:17:35.002
I'm just worried that life will be hard for her.

00:17:35.609 --> 00:17:38.373
The world can be cruel to her.

00:17:39.566 --> 00:17:41.345
Our daughter is strong.

00:17:41.625 --> 00:17:44.869
She's been through more than we realize.

00:17:45.757 --> 00:17:48.613
What she needs right now isn't our orders.

00:17:49.566 --> 00:17:51.866
It's someone to stand by her side.

00:18:04.900 --> 00:18:07.306
Invite Khun Charm to meet me at the house.

00:18:07.493 --> 00:18:09.587
And don't let Khun Pingrak know about this.

00:18:52.533 --> 00:18:53.540
Hello.

00:18:54.661 --> 00:18:55.604
Thank you

00:18:56.024 --> 00:18:58.256
for giving me the chance to speak with you today.

00:18:59.564 --> 00:19:01.692
Call me Khun Pornpima.

00:19:02.393 --> 00:19:04.292
I only have one daughter.

00:19:07.133 --> 00:19:07.933
Understood.

00:19:09.466 --> 00:19:10.733
Khun Pornpima.

00:19:12.200 --> 00:19:13.900
Let me ask you straight.

00:19:14.933 --> 00:19:16.666
Why did you come back to Ping?

00:19:17.300 --> 00:19:18.733
Because I love her.

00:19:20.733 --> 00:19:22.362
Even though in the past,

00:19:22.642 --> 00:19:24.812
I made her cry.

00:19:25.980 --> 00:19:26.646
But Ping

00:19:27.580 --> 00:19:30.073
is the only person I could never forget.

00:19:30.566 --> 00:19:33.957
So you came back to make things harder for my daughter?

00:19:34.191 --> 00:19:37.236
What makes you think you're better than Pat?

00:19:37.610 --> 00:19:39.874
I honestly can't see it.

00:19:41.200 --> 00:19:42.066
I have a job.

00:19:43.100 --> 00:19:43.900
I have a future.

00:19:45.066 --> 00:19:46.466
My intentions are clear.

00:19:46.800 --> 00:19:49.200
Because Ping is the only one I truly love.

00:19:50.900 --> 00:19:53.472
I'm not trying to compete with or beat anyone.

00:19:54.547 --> 00:19:56.021
But Ping

00:19:56.488 --> 00:19:58.933
is the only one I never stopped loving.

00:19:59.266 --> 00:20:00.578
I don't know

00:20:01.326 --> 00:20:04.361
if you're saying this because you actually mean it,

00:20:04.828 --> 00:20:07.368
or if you're just trying to win me over.

00:20:07.835 --> 00:20:09.455
But certainly,

00:20:09.782 --> 00:20:11.509
My daughter means everything to me.

00:20:11.900 --> 00:20:13.351
And I can't even tell you

00:20:13.351 --> 00:20:15.747
if I'll ever be able to accept you.

00:20:16.214 --> 00:20:18.125
Mark my words,

00:20:18.125 --> 00:20:22.433
don't you dare hurt my daughter again.

00:20:23.500 --> 00:20:24.300
Yes, ma'am.

00:20:25.566 --> 00:20:26.816
I promise

00:20:27.704 --> 00:20:30.588
that I'll protect her with my life.

00:20:55.800 --> 00:20:57.141
Oh, Ping.

00:20:57.141 --> 00:20:58.627
Are you here to see Charm?

00:20:58.627 --> 00:20:59.133
Hello.

00:20:59.400 --> 00:21:00.766
But she's not here.

00:21:01.800 --> 00:21:02.373
Then

00:21:02.700 --> 00:21:04.193
where did she go?

00:21:04.566 --> 00:21:06.594
She told me she had an important appointment.

00:21:06.594 --> 00:21:08.166
I thought she went to see you.

00:21:09.133 --> 00:21:10.600
Oh,

00:21:10.866 --> 00:21:13.100
it's okay. Thank you, P'Wan.

00:21:13.533 --> 00:21:14.333
You're welcome.

00:21:23.800 --> 00:21:24.600
Hello.

00:21:25.366 --> 00:21:28.000
Hey Ping, I was just about to call you.

00:21:28.533 --> 00:21:30.166
Where are you?

00:21:30.800 --> 00:21:32.134
I just finished my errands.

00:21:32.134 --> 00:21:34.133
I'm driving back to the mall to see you.

00:21:34.933 --> 00:21:37.266
Want to go get something good to eat tonight?

00:21:37.666 --> 00:21:40.533
Wait for me a bit, I'm almost there.

00:21:40.900 --> 00:21:42.766
Okay, see you soon.

00:21:53.800 --> 00:21:55.166
Was work tiring today?

00:21:55.766 --> 00:21:56.566
Not really.

00:21:59.600 --> 00:22:00.691
But...

00:22:01.672 --> 00:22:04.074
You're still stressing over your mom, aren't you?

00:22:09.200 --> 00:22:10.200
P'Charm.

00:22:11.000 --> 00:22:13.300
Ever since I called off the engagement with P'Pat,

00:22:14.400 --> 00:22:16.933
Mom hasn't talked to me normally at all.

00:22:21.166 --> 00:22:22.066
Ping.

00:22:24.333 --> 00:22:25.566
Earlier today when I was away,

00:22:28.566 --> 00:22:29.366
I actually

00:22:34.500 --> 00:22:36.400
went to talk to your mom.

00:22:39.500 --> 00:22:42.266
Did she say anything bad to you?

00:22:44.100 --> 00:22:44.900
No.

00:22:50.900 --> 00:22:52.146
But from now on,

00:22:52.894 --> 00:22:55.306
you have to leave this to me.

00:22:56.474 --> 00:22:57.776
I will prove

00:22:58.524 --> 00:23:00.221
to your family

00:23:00.828 --> 00:23:02.270
that I can truly love

00:23:03.485 --> 00:23:05.114
and take care of you.

00:23:06.866 --> 00:23:07.737
Does that mean

00:23:08.111 --> 00:23:10.474
Mom approves of our relationship now?

00:23:15.566 --> 00:23:16.586
Maybe

00:23:17.240 --> 00:23:18.662
not completely.

00:23:19.457 --> 00:23:20.891
But at least

00:23:22.059 --> 00:23:23.612
she's giving me a chance.

00:23:25.247 --> 00:23:26.442
So,

00:23:27.844 --> 00:23:30.000
you don't need to stress over this anymore.

00:23:35.266 --> 00:23:36.066
Come on.

00:23:38.066 --> 00:23:38.961
Today,

00:23:39.428 --> 00:23:41.678
I'm taking my girlfriend out.

00:23:42.052 --> 00:23:44.667
Want to grab some food at the night market?

00:23:45.466 --> 00:23:46.235
Let's go see

00:23:46.515 --> 00:23:49.346
if there's any mango sticky rice place you'll like.

00:23:49.766 --> 00:23:52.500
Then you have to treat me today.

00:23:52.733 --> 00:23:54.333
I'm going to eat the whole market.

00:23:55.600 --> 00:23:56.400
Of course.

00:23:57.600 --> 00:23:58.400
Let's go.

00:24:04.733 --> 00:24:09.366
Excuse me, I'll take a small size of this and add this.

00:24:13.500 --> 00:24:14.558
Today

00:24:15.072 --> 00:24:16.514
feels just like back then.

00:24:17.100 --> 00:24:18.022
Back then?

00:24:18.676 --> 00:24:20.673
When we snuck out together?

00:24:25.767 --> 00:24:26.512
Did you get it?

00:24:26.512 --> 00:24:27.366
I want fries too.

00:24:31.795 --> 00:24:32.766
You can just take it.

00:24:50.100 --> 00:24:51.266
Back off!

00:24:56.280 --> 00:24:57.405
Ping, Ping!

00:24:58.059 --> 00:24:58.707
Stay back!

00:24:59.066 --> 00:24:59.866
Ping!

00:25:27.200 --> 00:25:28.000
P'Charm!

00:25:28.700 --> 00:25:29.500
P'Charm!

00:25:30.066 --> 00:25:31.166
Stay with me!

00:25:54.266 --> 00:25:55.200
P'Charm!

00:25:57.566 --> 00:25:58.718
P'Charm!

00:25:58.718 --> 00:25:59.600
Help!

00:26:01.133 --> 00:26:02.500
Somebody please help!

00:26:02.700 --> 00:26:03.766
Please help P'Charm!

00:26:05.600 --> 00:26:07.066
Please help us!

00:26:08.933 --> 00:26:09.733
P'Charm!

00:26:26.000 --> 00:26:27.700
P'Charm, please hang in there!

00:26:35.533 --> 00:26:36.292
Ping!

00:26:36.292 --> 00:26:37.533
Where is Charm? What happened?

00:26:39.366 --> 00:26:40.900
P'Charm got shot.

00:26:41.766 --> 00:26:43.166
It's alright, it's alright.

00:26:43.353 --> 00:26:44.720
She's going to be fine.

00:26:51.600 --> 00:26:52.400
Ping.

00:26:53.066 --> 00:26:53.866
Ping, honey.

00:26:54.133 --> 00:26:55.866
Are you hurt?

00:26:56.966 --> 00:26:57.766
Mom.

00:26:58.666 --> 00:27:00.733
P'Charm took a bullet for me.

00:27:02.266 --> 00:27:04.600
Is she safe now?

00:27:05.300 --> 00:27:06.700
The doctors are treating her.

00:27:07.566 --> 00:27:09.166
I really don't know.

00:27:12.333 --> 00:27:15.533
Charm really kept the promise she made to me.

00:27:17.133 --> 00:27:18.337
I see it now.

00:27:18.711 --> 00:27:21.174
I know how much she loves you.

00:27:34.900 --> 00:27:36.170
The patient is safe now.

00:27:36.684 --> 00:27:39.672
The bullet went through her shoulder
but missed all vital organs.

00:27:40.466 --> 00:27:42.882
It's a good thing she was brought here in time.

00:27:43.303 --> 00:27:45.808
We've moved her to the recovery room.

00:27:46.229 --> 00:27:47.954
You can visit her now.

00:28:03.200 --> 00:28:05.368
Currently, Khun Chalisa's condition

00:28:05.695 --> 00:28:07.185
is nothing to worry about.

00:28:08.073 --> 00:28:11.087
Only the wound is still a little inflamed.

00:28:23.434 --> 00:28:25.103
P'Charm.

00:28:51.466 --> 00:28:52.266
P'Charm.

00:28:56.500 --> 00:28:57.933
Are you hurt anywhere?

00:28:58.900 --> 00:29:00.100
I'm completely fine.

00:29:01.533 --> 00:29:02.733
It's you.

00:29:04.600 --> 00:29:05.700
Does it hurt a lot?

00:29:11.666 --> 00:29:12.566
Just a little bit.

00:29:21.600 --> 00:29:23.566
I thought you said it didn't hurt?

00:30:02.200 --> 00:30:03.367
Mom.

00:30:03.601 --> 00:30:05.200
P'Charm is awake.

00:30:08.500 --> 00:30:10.700
You saved my daughter's life.

00:30:11.766 --> 00:30:12.733
Thank you so much.

00:30:17.966 --> 00:30:19.333
Don't get up.

00:30:20.600 --> 00:30:22.166
Your wound still hurts.

00:30:23.466 --> 00:30:24.849
I can hardly believe

00:30:25.223 --> 00:30:29.103
that someone would take a bullet
for the person they love,

00:30:29.710 --> 00:30:31.240
except in a soap opera.

00:30:31.933 --> 00:30:33.933
If you truly love my daughter,

00:30:34.800 --> 00:30:37.566
if you're ready to stay by her side

00:30:38.333 --> 00:30:40.000
no matter what happens...

00:30:41.200 --> 00:30:44.466
I have no reason to get in the way anymore.

00:30:49.300 --> 00:30:50.100
Thank you.

00:30:51.900 --> 00:30:54.466
I promise I will take the best care of her.

00:30:56.566 --> 00:30:58.166
Thank you, Khun Pornpima.

00:31:00.133 --> 00:31:01.434
From now on,

00:31:01.808 --> 00:31:03.389
I forbid you

00:31:03.623 --> 00:31:05.407
from calling me Khun Pornpima.

00:31:11.762 --> 00:31:13.143
You can call me Mom now.

00:31:32.166 --> 00:31:33.133
I'll get going now.

00:31:46.733 --> 00:31:48.858
You just woke up.

00:31:49.185 --> 00:31:50.562
Do you want to eat anything?

00:31:50.936 --> 00:31:53.513
Do you want an apple? I can peel one for you.

00:31:54.133 --> 00:31:55.154
No thanks.

00:31:56.089 --> 00:31:57.813
You might cut yourself.

00:31:59.466 --> 00:32:00.886
How about an orange?

00:32:00.886 --> 00:32:01.766
I can go buy some.

00:32:02.300 --> 00:32:03.733
I don't like oranges.

00:32:05.733 --> 00:32:06.729
Then

00:32:07.850 --> 00:32:10.000
what do you want to eat?

00:32:11.500 --> 00:32:13.266
Come closer.

00:32:19.400 --> 00:32:21.100
I'd rather eat you up.

00:32:29.366 --> 00:32:30.166
Take that.

00:32:30.900 --> 00:32:31.900
Ouch!

00:32:33.100 --> 00:32:34.666
I thought you said it didn't hurt?

00:32:48.933 --> 00:32:50.066
The other side too.

00:33:21.300 --> 00:33:22.100
Mom!

00:33:22.733 --> 00:33:24.533
Charm, how are you doing?

00:33:25.000 --> 00:33:25.800
Ouch.

00:33:26.166 --> 00:33:27.500
Does it still hurt a lot?

00:33:28.166 --> 00:33:30.133
I'm sorry I'm late.

00:33:31.733 --> 00:33:33.140
I'm so happy

00:33:34.028 --> 00:33:35.314
that you're back.

00:34:05.166 --> 00:34:08.266
If I could take your place, I would.

00:34:09.900 --> 00:34:11.442
Just having you here

00:34:12.704 --> 00:34:14.866
makes me really happy.

00:34:15.733 --> 00:34:16.800
I'm happy too.

00:34:19.533 --> 00:34:20.418
I am

00:34:21.119 --> 00:34:24.167
so proud of how brave you are.

00:34:30.000 --> 00:34:36.392
It feels like a dream to be with you again, Mom.

00:34:39.400 --> 00:34:40.400
This is delicious, Mom.

00:34:41.000 --> 00:34:41.900
Thank you, dear.

00:34:43.325 --> 00:34:47.227
And it makes me feel like I'm not alone anymore.

00:35:06.733 --> 00:35:07.560
Hello.

00:35:07.934 --> 00:35:09.374
Feel free to look around.

00:35:18.500 --> 00:35:19.366
Feel free to browse.

00:36:23.400 --> 00:36:25.533
Happy Valentine's Day, P'Wan.

00:36:27.666 --> 00:36:28.466
Thank you.

00:36:34.700 --> 00:36:35.500
Smells so good.

00:36:40.900 --> 00:36:42.166
Why are you staring at me?

00:36:43.200 --> 00:36:46.466
Don't you have anything for me, P'Wan?

00:36:50.066 --> 00:36:50.866
Hmm?

00:36:51.900 --> 00:36:54.500
You never change, do you?

00:36:55.800 --> 00:36:58.966
I really am the same after all these years.

00:36:59.700 --> 00:37:00.500
Alright, alright.

00:37:00.966 --> 00:37:02.800
Close your eyes first.

00:37:05.100 --> 00:37:06.166
A surprise?

00:37:07.266 --> 00:37:08.066
Yeah.

00:37:08.766 --> 00:37:09.566
What is it?

00:37:15.300 --> 00:37:16.100
I love you.

00:37:35.100 --> 00:37:37.933
Then after we're done hanging out with P'Charm tonight,

00:37:40.000 --> 00:37:41.734
can I sleep over at your place?

00:38:23.700 --> 00:38:25.066
Happy Valentine's Day.

00:38:37.600 --> 00:38:38.966
Thank you, P'Charm.

00:38:40.000 --> 00:38:41.400
Happy Valentine's Day.

00:38:44.133 --> 00:38:45.533
You look so beautiful today.

00:38:46.566 --> 00:38:48.166
Am I not beautiful on other days?

00:38:51.100 --> 00:38:52.068
By the way,

00:38:53.189 --> 00:38:55.289
you don't have chocolates for me today

00:38:55.710 --> 00:38:57.000
like when we were kids?

00:38:57.654 --> 00:38:58.563
P'Charm!

00:38:59.600 --> 00:39:00.666
I'm just kidding.

00:39:02.100 --> 00:39:03.466
But even if you gave me some,

00:39:04.133 --> 00:39:05.400
I wouldn't accept it anyway.

00:39:11.166 --> 00:39:12.700
Because I'd rather have you.

00:39:17.100 --> 00:39:19.666
You're laying it on a bit thick, Khun Charm.

00:39:20.200 --> 00:39:21.666
I'm going to throw up.

00:39:34.866 --> 00:39:35.700
Ping.

00:39:38.733 --> 00:39:39.920
Even though

00:39:41.415 --> 00:39:43.426
I might not be the most perfect person,

00:39:46.100 --> 00:39:47.279
but I promise

00:39:48.260 --> 00:39:49.714
to love

00:39:52.300 --> 00:39:54.100
and take the best care of you.

00:40:47.466 --> 00:40:48.566
Will you marry me?

00:41:04.166 --> 00:41:04.932
Yes.

00:42:32.533 --> 00:42:34.767
Thank you for the flowers, P'Charm.

00:42:35.655 --> 00:42:36.840
They're beautiful.

00:42:48.366 --> 00:42:49.722
Do you know?

00:42:50.096 --> 00:42:52.853
Since the first day you walked into my life,

00:42:54.909 --> 00:42:56.427
my world

00:42:58.266 --> 00:42:59.800
hasn't been the same.

00:43:01.366 --> 00:43:03.235
If you mean

00:43:03.515 --> 00:43:04.646
it got more chaotic,

00:43:05.733 --> 00:43:07.066
I'll admit to that.

00:43:10.133 --> 00:43:10.933
No.

00:43:11.933 --> 00:43:14.166
But truly loving someone

00:43:15.733 --> 00:43:17.266
takes effort

00:43:20.166 --> 00:43:21.766
and sacrifice.

00:43:24.866 --> 00:43:26.041
Thank you

00:43:26.508 --> 00:43:27.759
for loving me.

00:43:28.733 --> 00:43:29.733
I don't just love you,

00:43:33.166 --> 00:43:35.036
but I'll keep you

00:43:37.793 --> 00:43:39.780
in my life forever.

00:43:40.366 --> 00:43:41.735
P'Charm.

00:43:43.090 --> 00:43:44.367
All this time,

00:43:45.700 --> 00:43:47.466
we've been through so much together.

00:43:48.600 --> 00:43:49.666
Good times,

00:43:51.166 --> 00:43:51.966
bad times,

00:43:53.400 --> 00:43:54.200
rumors,

00:43:55.466 --> 00:43:56.300
and fear.

00:43:57.700 --> 00:43:59.533
So many times I almost gave up.

00:44:00.500 --> 00:44:02.866
But having you right by my side

00:44:04.700 --> 00:44:06.300
gave me the courage to love.

00:44:09.700 --> 00:44:11.400
Now we aren't afraid of anything anymore.

00:44:20.266 --> 00:44:22.566
Because we got through it together.

00:44:24.700 --> 00:44:26.040
Through the

00:44:26.367 --> 00:44:27.527
smiles,

00:44:31.466 --> 00:44:32.400
the tears,

00:44:34.966 --> 00:44:36.166
and the misunderstandings.

00:44:38.000 --> 00:44:40.100
But it was all worth it.

00:44:41.566 --> 00:44:42.366
Because

00:44:43.533 --> 00:44:45.400
it brought us to where we are today.

00:45:21.537 --> 00:45:22.674
Wow, so romantic! I'm crying!

00:45:22.908 --> 00:45:24.292
Truly admirable courage. Love is love.

00:45:24.292 --> 00:45:25.586
The ship has finally sailed. I'm so proud!

00:45:26.240 --> 00:45:27.856
Marrying another woman these days

00:45:27.856 --> 00:45:29.090
is understandable.

00:45:29.090 --> 00:45:30.825
But are they really right for each other?

00:45:30.825 --> 00:45:32.825
One is the owner of a mall,

00:45:32.825 --> 00:45:34.451
while the other clearly hit the jackpot.

00:45:40.000 --> 00:45:41.344
Exactly, I thought the same thing.

00:45:41.344 --> 00:45:43.235
That's a bit harsh, but they have a point.

00:46:24.600 --> 00:46:25.500
P'Charm?

00:46:30.533 --> 00:46:31.533
Are you awake?

00:46:32.366 --> 00:46:33.166
Yes.

00:46:33.566 --> 00:46:34.700
Do you know?

00:46:36.066 --> 00:46:36.966
That last night,

00:46:39.300 --> 00:46:40.300
I was so scared.

00:46:41.800 --> 00:46:42.800
Scared of what?

00:46:43.766 --> 00:46:46.733
I was scared that last night

00:46:48.200 --> 00:46:49.400
was just a dream.

00:46:51.333 --> 00:46:52.538
P'Charm.

00:46:53.800 --> 00:46:55.556
Do you believe it now?

00:46:56.257 --> 00:46:58.267
That I'm really here with you?

00:46:58.800 --> 00:46:59.900
I love you, Ping.

00:47:01.300 --> 00:47:02.866
I love you the most.

00:47:03.800 --> 00:47:05.866
I missed you like this every night.

00:47:07.366 --> 00:47:08.466
Like what?

00:47:13.333 --> 00:47:14.133
Like this.
(Ping) P'Charm!

00:47:14.800 --> 00:47:15.600
And this.

00:47:18.533 --> 00:47:19.566
P'Charm!

00:47:30.000 --> 00:47:30.818
P'Charm...

00:47:30.966 --> 00:47:31.766
Let me kiss you.

00:47:40.500 --> 00:47:41.811
Right now, the news about you

00:47:41.811 --> 00:47:43.933
is a hot topic on social media.

00:47:44.133 --> 00:47:46.054
If it were just about the two of us,

00:47:46.054 --> 00:47:47.733
things wouldn't be this hard.

00:47:48.300 --> 00:47:51.266
Why is it so hard to just marry the person you love?

00:47:51.733 --> 00:47:53.600
Do you really not know what to do?

00:47:54.166 --> 00:47:55.673
You have a great helper.

00:47:55.673 --> 00:47:57.533
I think it's time you use it.

00:47:58.366 --> 00:48:00.623
I might not be the most perfect person.

00:48:00.623 --> 00:48:03.020
But having you

00:48:03.020 --> 00:48:04.900
makes me the luckiest person in the world.